data.title: Decadent Sympozium - Lux Invictus
data.description:
► Subscribe: http://bit.ly/SubscribeNeogoa

After eight months of hard work, we’re happy to finally introduce our third installment of Dimensional Gateway, with almost 80 minutes of high-quality psychedelic trance music from some of the best artists in the modern Goa trance genre. Download Dimensional Gateway 3 - http://www.neogoa.net/dimensional-gateway-3/

Tracklist:

01 - PharaOm - Space Outpost Titan V (142 BPM) 
02 - Trinodia - 7th Ace (139 BPM)

05 - Decadent Sympozium - Lux Invictus (144 BPM)
